auth-url:export.description:
Print a Sfdx Auth Url.
This is a wrapper for sfdx force:org:display --verbose.

loglevel.name: loglevel
loglevel.description: logging level for this command invocation

targetusername.name: targetusername

apiversion.description: override the api version used for api requests made by this command

auth-url:import.description:
Authorize an org.
This is a wrapper for sfdx force:auth:sfdxurl:store without requiring a sfdxAuthUrl file.

loglevel.name: loglevel
loglevel.description: logging level for this command invocation

setalias.name: setalias
setalias.description: set an alias for the authenticated org

setdefaultdevhubusername.description: set the authenticated org as the default dev hub org for scratch org creation

setdefaultusername.description: set the authenticated org as the default username that all commands run against
